!! It is a sublist of Yet another small uBlock filter list
! See https://github.com/mtxadmin/ublock for details
!
!
!! Many fast general rules, compacting site headers to improve readability and minimize unnecessary scrolling
!! Yes, all these rules were based on in-the-wild sites and therefore they are very useful
! 
! First: removing logos and images from top. 
!
! Second: unstick headers, top menus etc
!
! Third: removing annoying page backgrounds
! 
! See some examples in _headers_examples (commented and not included in the whole list, just for information and backup)
!
! This is v2 version, more compact one. See v1 filterset in _headers_old - bulky, but working and time-proved
!
!
! See cosmetic rules policy at https://github.com/mtxadmin/ublock/blob/master/docs/policy_en.md
!
! Something doesn't work? Something is missing? Please, feel free to write about it here:
! https://github.com/mtxadmin/ublock/issues/new



!! headers and header logos
!   in general, do not block ###header, ###masthead, ##.site-branding or similar - they often contain search and menus
!   of course, there may be some exclusions here (but it is unlikely)
!   below there are some of old logo rules, just for information
-logo-$image,domain=~opera.com
    ! Exclusions:
    ! opera - bad interface on opera.com, no alternative texts
    !
    ! -logo-line.$image
-logo.$image,domain=~factorio.fandom.com|~opera.com
    ! Exclusions:
    ! Factorio wiki - useful interface elements
    ! opera - bad interface on opera.com, no alternative texts
    !
    ! /-logo.gif/
    ! /-logo.jpg/
    ! /-logo.png/
    ! /-logo.svg/
/_logo_/$image
    ! /vbulletin3_logo_white.png
_logo_$image
_logo.$image,domain=~factorio.fandom.com|~opera.com
    ! Exclusions:
    ! Factorio wiki - useful interface elements
    ! opera - bad interface on opera.com, no alternative texts
    !
    ! /adaptive_logo.png
    ! /_logo.gif/
    !     !/site_logo.gif
    !         ! PhpBB: /forum/styles/subsilver2/imageset/site_logo.gif
    ! /_logo.jpg/
    ! /_logo.png/
    !     ! /site_logo.png
    !     ! /small_logo.png
    ! /_logo.svg/
